Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.37,0:00:06.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.74,0:00:08.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.00,0:00:17.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.09,0:00:26.49,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We've left the established course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.51,0:00:30.08,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're rowing straight toward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.10,0:00:35.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The borderline between the sky and the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.65,0:00:41.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,In the dark depths of the ocean,\Nadventure holds its breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.78,0:00:48.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a good time just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.58,0:00:53.02,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.04,0:00:55.32,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.34,0:01:03.34,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.43,0:01:12.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"That feeling" I get when embarking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.85,0:01:16.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something I hope to remember always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.40,0:01:21.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can, I won't be afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.99,0:01:28.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,With our pulses racing, \Nlet's go on a trip now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.12,0:01:34.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Shy hearts engrave the rhythm of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.87,0:01:39.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.42,0:01:41.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.67,0:01:45.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.01,0:01:49.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.06,0:01:50.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is "Adventurous"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.68,0:01:52.37,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Be aware it's "Dangerous"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.39,0:01:54.08,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna be "One of us"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.10,0:01:55.71,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And a trip goes on because
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.73,0:01:57.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We da pirate of the "Mass"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.40,0:01:59.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,To the West, To the East
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.07,0:02:00.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta find my way, Sail away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.44,0:02:01.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,All the way to "One piece"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.53,0:02:05.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff a dream into your empty chest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.91,0:02:08.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And spread your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.20,0:02:12.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If the wind blowing through\Nthem dyes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.54,0:02:14.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's press forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.71,0:02:19.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.09,0:02:21.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.42,0:02:25.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.76,0:02:32.13,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.15,0:02:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the voyage to their next destination,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.32,0:02:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and crew drop by\Nthe resort ship, Spa Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.02,0:02:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While enjoying their vacation,\Nthey meet the sisters Sayo and Rina.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.19,0:02:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the ocean raccoon dog, Nukki.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.63,0:02:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sis Sayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.00,0:02:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're doomed now that\NI've run into you, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.44,0:03:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.29,0:03:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum Bazooka!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.22,0:03:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about that notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.62,0:03:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Foxy and his goons are after it, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.89,0:03:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This notebook explains how to create jewels!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.66,0:03:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, please help--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.29,0:03:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and crew managed\Nto repel the Foxy Crew,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.56,0:03:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which was after the sisters' notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.47,0:03:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It held the secret to their father's\Nresearch on making jewels.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.44,0:03:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now Sayo has been taken hostage\Nby the mastermind, Doran!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.96,0:03:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Great Scramble for Treasure!\NCollapse! Spa Island!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.42,0:03:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sis Sayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.44,0:03:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dang! This ship is loaded with traps.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.20,0:04:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.10,0:04:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was pathetic, "Silver Fox" Foxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.91,0:04:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They won despite your trickery.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.84,0:04:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well. Now I simply have to wait for\Nthem to solve the secret of the jewels.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.62,0:04:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This just isn't enough to go by!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.79,0:04:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you search all over the ship?\NWasn't there a large "X" mark?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.05,0:04:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.97,0:04:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This notebook really is full of lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.94,0:04:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now my sister is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.88,0:04:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Luffy!\N--Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.85,0:04:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please save... Big Sis Sayo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.12,0:04:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.05,0:04:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You're sure? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.69,0:04:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I wanna see those jewels.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.03,0:05:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though this notebook could be lying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.29,0:05:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how are we going to save her, Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.65,0:05:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... Why don't we destroy this ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.04,0:05:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whaaat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.50,0:05:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.88,0:05:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did that come from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.71,0:05:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, man! Are you thinking straight?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.61,0:05:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Sayo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.83,0:05:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll find her if we destroy the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.71,0:05:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the hint about the jewels?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.11,0:05:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be easier to look for if we destroy the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.65,0:05:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.09,0:05:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.12,0:05:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no point worrying about something
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.45,0:05:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nthat might not be on this ship, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.83,0:05:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear, you guys don't\Nhave a shred of delicacy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.48,0:05:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san, the idea of meekly obeying
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.95,0:05:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nthat dastardly mustache irks me to no end.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.69,0:05:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if we sink this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.96,0:05:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gah! Not you too, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.97,0:05:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't someone going to stop them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.36,0:05:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those were the Captain's orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.27,0:05:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're quick on the uptake!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.25,0:05:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.13,0:05:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please look after Sunny.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.75,0:05:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.22,0:06:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Super!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.22,0:06:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There goes the resort...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.52,0:06:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Destroy this ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.79,0:06:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,108-Pound Phoenix!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.80,0:06:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Concasser!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.64,0:06:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum Whip!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.78,0:06:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tabasco Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.68,0:06:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hoofprint Roseo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.63,0:06:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thunderbolt Tempo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.76,0:06:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clutch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.76,0:06:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three-Pace Hum... Notch Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.05,0:06:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.89,0:06:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give Sayo back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.46,0:06:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Outta my way! Move! Move! Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.97,0:06:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like those puny bullets can hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.06,0:06:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.54,0:07:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He repelled the bullets?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.55,0:07:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Owie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.11,0:07:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jerks! Now I'm ticked!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.37,0:07:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weapons Left!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.34,0:07:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Come on and give Sayo back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.41,0:07:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Curse you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.74,0:07:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.62,0:07:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a cannon?! I thought it was a chimney!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.55,0:08:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.76,0:08:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rina!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.79,0:08:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! He's taken her hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.97,0:08:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you wreak havoc on my ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.66,0:08:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you realize how much\Nit cost to build Spa Island?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.57,0:08:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn that rotten mustached jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.10,0:09:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.80,0:09:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.84,0:09:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sis Sayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.71,0:09:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next I'm gonna blow that brat sky high!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.65,0:09:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.82,0:09:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had originally wanted you to\Nsolve the puzzle in that notebook,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.86,0:09:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but forget it! I'll be taking that notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.90,0:09:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give her back after you hand it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.39,0:09:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can have the notebook,\Nso give Big Sis Sayo back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.80,0:09:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.97,0:09:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give it to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.31,0:09:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sis Sayo...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.98,0:09:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rina, solve the secret in the notebook\Nand finish Dad's research!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.92,0:09:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Why should I?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.66,0:09:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe in Dad, Rina!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.02,0:09:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give Dad's research to that jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.79,0:09:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad was working to make his
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.87,0:10:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,dream come true for you, me, and everyone in the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.60,0:10:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! For my sake,\Ndon't throw away Dad's dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.72,0:10:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lying! Dad is just\Na self-absorbed researcher.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.08,0:10:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rina...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.36,0:10:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean... I mean, he was\Nalways in his own world!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.42,0:10:23.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"For Dad"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.88,0:10:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's done!\N--It's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.82,0:10:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think Dad will like his birthday cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.23,0:10:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.27,0:10:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He isn't coming home!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.97,0:10:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he must have found something again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.91,0:10:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.91,0:10:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.04,0:11:14.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"For Dad"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.67,0:11:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A cake? Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.60,0:11:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They must have baked a cake for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.25,0:11:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.41,0:11:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I wake you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.62,0:11:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are these?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.92,0:11:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cast-off Thirty Year Cicada shells.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.56,0:11:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NI can probably use them in my research.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.38,0:11:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a big outbreak of them\Nfor the first time in thirty years!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.06,0:11:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right? Ah! But last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.73,0:11:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A cake! That cake looks delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.36,0:11:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that cake...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.04,0:11:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We made that yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.65,0:12:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It may have gone bad. It is summer and all...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.79,0:12:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor... Get a doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.32,0:12:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He already saw you and left!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.27,0:12:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about him!\NHe doesn't know a thing about us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.70,0:12:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't think about us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.35,0:12:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this isn't the time to get in a fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.43,0:12:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't butt in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.97,0:12:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is their problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.69,0:12:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rina, you're mistaken! Listen to me! Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.72,0:12:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry about the cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.35,0:12:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.69,0:12:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were looking forward to having\Na birthday party, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.86,0:12:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.02,0:12:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need the materials in the
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.84,0:12:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,cast-off Thirty Year Cicada shells to make the jewels.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.80,0:12:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I didn't get them now, I'd have\Nto wait another thirty years...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.57,0:12:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.40,0:12:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.70,0:12:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.41,0:13:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.76,0:13:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. But I bet Rina is mad at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.91,0:13:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are just like your mother,\Nbut Rina takes after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.62,0:13:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a handful when she gets upset!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.72,0:13:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After I make some jewels,\Nlet's eat a cake that's this big!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.93,0:13:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.00,0:13:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get one that Rina could hide in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.74,0:13:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nukki says that it's all true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.17,0:13:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he said that your father\Nleft home to protect you and Sayo
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.21,0:13:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from some bad guys who\Nwere after his jewel research.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.20,0:13:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.19,0:13:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.28,0:13:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't find one...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.83,0:14:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to work to find a four-leaf clover.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.70,0:14:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Big Sis found three of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.79,0:14:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because she believed with all
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.56,0:14:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nof her heart that she would find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.87,0:14:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--She believed?\N--Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.77,0:14:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conducting research and searching\Nfor four-leaf clovers are similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.64,0:14:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you never stop believing and work hard,\Nit will pay off in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.52,0:14:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Then I'm going to find a five-leaf clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.53,0:14:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Five leaves...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.60,0:14:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'd be amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.17,0:14:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found one!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.37,0:14:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found a five-leaf clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.69,0:14:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's... Rina!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.00,0:14:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were right! I believed I could find one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.50,0:14:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Rina! That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.62,0:14:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.02,0:15:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Rina! I'm gonna\Nsucceed with my research!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.06,0:15:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... I had forgotten all about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.19,0:15:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I used to believe he could pull it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.27,0:15:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Dad's dream! It has to come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.34,0:15:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rina!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.56,0:15:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've changed my mind! You can't\Nhave the notebook after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.16,0:15:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.32,0:15:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's show time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.50,0:15:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't play games with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.34,0:15:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seis Fleurs!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.61,0:15:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tabasco Star Onslaught! Star! Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.71,0:15:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami, get on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.85,0:15:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.56,0:16:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayo-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.52,0:16:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! Untie her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.69,0:16:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.14,0:16:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lock?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.37,0:16:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.59,0:16:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.59,0:16:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.51,0:16:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three-Sword Style...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.95,0:16:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Great Buddha Slayer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.85,0:16:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're doing a great job.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.23,0:16:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you need to do a great job!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.27,0:16:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Curse you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.61,0:16:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.28,0:17:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The jerk! He released all\Nof the steam in the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.06,0:17:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's better!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.69,0:17:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.55,0:17:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Rina!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.94,0:17:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.66,0:17:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Third Gear!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.78,0:17:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bone Balloon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.82,0:17:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Giant Axe!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.64,0:18:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.15,0:18:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth is going on...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.52,0:18:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.42,0:18:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.44,0:18:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid! Don't forget about\Neveryone who has to abandon ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.88,0:18:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, you're amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.25,0:18:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops! I forgot that I shrink\Nwhen I use that move.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.14,0:18:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.56,0:19:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh! Think ahead a little, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.68,0:19:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A giant "X."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.66,0:19:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.03,0:19:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Serves the jerk right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.34,0:19:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An "X"! And it's huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.61,0:19:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep! Dad was referring to that\Nunderwater volcano on the map.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.78,0:19:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doran built his ship right above\Nthe treasure he was searching for.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.58,0:19:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The doof didn't realize the key\Nto the secret was right under him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.84,0:20:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.20,0:20:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's... a circular rainbow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.77,0:20:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen a round rainbow before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.58,0:20:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.35,0:20:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a mysterious rainbow! Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.15,0:20:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a sec! Is that the treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.34,0:20:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.02,0:20:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, circular rainbows\Nare referred to as the "ocean's treasure."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.90,0:20:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.26,0:20:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.34,0:20:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.97,0:20:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You better not tell me that this is the treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.01,0:20:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.54,0:20:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.65,0:20:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can have all of the treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.32,0:20:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give us that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.02,0:21:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? That rainbow looks weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.65,0:21:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The order of the colors is inversed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.92,0:21:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The order...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.13,0:21:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.36,0:21:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.76,0:21:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"-Several Days Later-"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.14,0:21:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that might be...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.45,0:21:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the monster raccoon dog\Nfrom the other day!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.54,0:21:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's an ocean raccoon dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.75,0:21:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.93,0:21:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like Sayo-chan's guess\Nwas dead on back there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.63,0:21:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Dear Luffy and friends. Are you well?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.73,0:21:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My big sister and I went straight\Nhome and tested out her idea."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.64,0:21:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We followed my father's formulas\Nand made seven different medications.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.67,0:22:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we mixed them together in\Nthe order of the circular rainbow...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.66,0:22:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.28,0:22:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She says it created a jewel!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.66,0:22:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! We did it! We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.12,0:22:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayo... Rina...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.45,0:22:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.41,0:22:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.94,0:22:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a sign of their gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.75,0:22:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say, "Thank you, guys."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.51,0:22:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me get a better look at it, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.18,0:22:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I wanna see it! Lemme see!\N--Huh? Let's see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.25,0:22:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Just a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.76,0:22:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys! This isn't a toy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.93,0:22:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.36,0:22:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's candy rain! Ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.37,0:22:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.70,0:22:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops. I dropped the jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.13,0:22:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Which one is it?!\N--Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.61,0:22:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! Find it fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.71,0:23:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys had better find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.95,0:23:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.45,0:23:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so excited, Brook?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.59,0:23:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After learning about the great feats\Nyou've accomplished on your voyage,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.79,0:23:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've realized I must work\Nto become a true comrade!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.31,0:23:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A true comrade"? That's not\Nsomething you work toward.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.58,0:23:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.87,0:23:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.27,0:23:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Brook's Great Struggle! Is the Path to\NBecoming a True Comrade Rigorous?"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.97,0:23:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
